{"tid":2100051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記唔記得大家講過「出解放軍就返屋企訓覺」，後黨安法時代，我哋要改變國際線進行嘅方式","createTime":"2020-07-08T17:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T04:04:00.000Z","uid":200019,"like":125,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"d5666fee8aeac861fcb3848cd4b8fa15bed30ba4","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">前言</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢一年我哋抗爭行動嘅目標不嬲都係攬炒<br />\n我並唔認為掟汽油彈就可以成功結束中共統治。我哋遊行我哋勇武我哋開花，最終都係圍繞住一個方針，製造壓力，製造憲政、管治同經濟危機。<br />\n<br />\n國安法就係我哋製造呢三個危機後所達致令中共撕爛塊面嘅終極後果。對唔住，香港人真係無能力逼出解放軍啦，但國安法仍然係一張通往「攬炒」嘅單程票，大家會唔會接受到袋住先？<br />\n<br />\n我哋再上街係為咗咩，再製造一次憲政同管治危機？我認為再製造更多嘅憲政同管治危機，對於出咗宇宙中共維護法都唔會再逼得出啲咩。我唔會同你講上定唔上，但有更重要嘅事要做。<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊要做嘅應該全力同中共進行經濟戰，走資<del>走人</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加速加速再加速，進行<strong><span class=\"x-large\">海外遊說，接觸當地支持我哋嘅民間團體同議員，以當地人身份製作以當地人為本位講中共存在對當地人嘅禍害嘅宣傳影片。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">正文</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我認為從頭到尾，香港人有香港人嘅責任其他國家嘅人有其他國家嘅人嘅責任。<br />\n<br />\n中國唔單止危害香港人嘅自由同人權，佢仲危害住世界所有人<br />\n<br />\n由<br />\n一帶一路債務陷阱外交<br />\n加拿大人質外交<br />\n澳洲國家級網絡攻擊<br />\n滲入美國媒體，影響大選<br />\n盜取知識產權<br />\n台海危機<br />\n南海軍事化<br />\n18國土地爭端<br />\n宇宙中共維護法<br />\n湄公河水壩下遊乾旱<br />\n低人權優勢，令各國產業流失，造成失業造成勞工利益受損<br />\n甚至乎惡意隱瞞疫情，中國境内停航，但國際航班keep going，做成全球50萬人死亡，講緊嘅係我哋200萬人嘅4份1<br />\n<br />\n如果種種以上都無辦法令各國下定決心，唔通死10萬個香港人，就會令各國下定決心？<br />\n<br />\n我哋香港人好可能最終會被消滅，而世界人民最終都係會承受到綏靖中共所帶嚟嘅苦果，世界人民係時候為捍衛佢哋自己嘅價值，捍衛佢嘅自己嘅生活方式而作出選擇。<br />\n<br />\n我哋要改變，我哋唔應該再話香港人點慘，而係接觸當地支持我哋嘅民間團體，接觸當哋支持我哋嘅議員，用佢哋嘅身份，用佢哋嘅媒體，企係佢哋嘅立場，話比佢哋知佢哋要正視呢件事。係一件關乎佢哋自己嘅事，而唔係一個遙遠東亞土地上嘅事。"},{"pid":"e85d739d23352e100eb92298ec4731dfce29a4ab","tid":2100051,"uid":154486,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:56:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">要打國際線<br />\n<strong>要加要初選出黎投票</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有民意backup既人，出黎國際講野都大聲D"},{"pid":"78981b995933a71b6e9f20b7009203d7b70d7493","tid":2100051,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e85d739d23352e100eb92298ec4731dfce29a4ab","tid":2100051,"uid":154486,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:56:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">要打國際線<br />\n<strong>要加要初選出黎投票</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有民意backup既人，出黎國際講野都大聲D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:56:32.000Z","msg":"更*"},{"pid":"ed0d90d454ed43bfb0ca80f0a5684d0a8a2714b3","tid":2100051,"uid":359260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"P牌支持香港再出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdf7b27f9592b0715d6402a5841eafb57ad6a92","tid":2100051,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:59:22.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"7fe038f5c34b52cc7d6659c815411df6a9878fbf","tid":2100051,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:00:05.000Z","msg":"推post推post"},{"pid":"82a9cd3641982b685a821e601cccd45afc2bbb93","tid":2100051,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:00:49.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"8fa64e4f7fb30778b9037809731acd9206313ee4","tid":2100051,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:01:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"55c87c7cf751e659b5534c47aaec62d2916cb279","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e85d739d23352e100eb92298ec4731dfce29a4ab","tid":2100051,"uid":154486,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:56:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">要打國際線<br />\n<strong>要加要初選出黎投票</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有民意backup既人，出黎國際講野都大聲D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"其實同我講嘅同一件事，初選固然要支持。<br />\n選出嚟嘅Icon代表我哋香港人，講香港事<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得我哋要用另一種方式滲入佢哋嘅民間，唔係用我哋嘅Icon，而係用佢哋嘅身份，講佢哋嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以依賴晒政治人物，我哋要自己做。<br />\n唔止要一個攬炒團隊唔止要一個袁弓夷(佢哋面向政要)，我要更多更多嘅秘密團隊去接觸民間團體。"},{"pid":"1793b13ef7ec9553709c394af03e68803d595803","tid":2100051,"uid":249794,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:03:09.000Z","msg":"以某部分思想黎講<br />\n佢地會覺得出解放軍仲唔出黎係淆底放棄抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688d4639472028279ab51a19fda175524b4909ff","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"55c87c7cf751e659b5534c47aaec62d2916cb279","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e85d739d23352e100eb92298ec4731dfce29a4ab","tid":2100051,"uid":154486,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:56:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">要打國際線<br />\n<strong>要加要初選出黎投票</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有民意backup既人，出黎國際講野都大聲D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"其實同我講嘅同一件事，初選固然要支持。<br />\n選出嚟嘅Icon代表我哋香港人，講香港事<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得我哋要用另一種方式滲入佢哋嘅民間，唔係用我哋嘅Icon，而係用佢哋嘅身份，講佢哋嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以依賴晒政治人物，我哋要自己做。<br />\n唔止要一個攬炒團隊唔止要一個袁弓夷(佢哋面向政要)，我要更多更多嘅秘密團隊去接觸民間團體。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:06:03.000Z","msg":"唔係同一件事*"},{"pid":"b11e4d512b11f798dc48c9b5864e3981a386eb3d","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:10:24.000Z","msg":"我太大壓力啦，打到手都震晒，但我都好努力要出呢個Post。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">我哋要改變！</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">我哋要改變！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c5a287d2f71952cc6216ce3c6217ab8dba984fb6","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:12:54.000Z","msg":"勇氣智慧也永不滅<br />\n<br />\n除左勇氣，我哋要更多嘅智慧去做呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96004bcf14981efcf36815cb8ceb6cc0add255db","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:16:35.000Z","msg":"求推，我內心有個聲音，我一定要努力推呢個Post。<br />\n我自己可能無能力做呢件事，一定要有人努力做好呢件事。"},{"pid":"3dc94cca0c79f0f8afb7a6277ce707595f08f2aa","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:19:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e19a730c72f8d9978903fe63ea0a393730a27440","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:20:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d795856d875ed491f4a6ca1a6e7c35cb14c60cc","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:25:09.000Z","msg":"大家可能會不滿我提倡走難，貶低咗街頭<br />\n但重點係改變國際戰線打嘅方式。<br />\n<br />\n就算你哋唔肯走，想上街都同呢個post無衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31143ff82fe7c3780b85198b1c1eaa5f7f71623b","tid":2100051,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:25:41.000Z","msg":"諗下諗下 其實外國國旗當衫著出街都幾好睇"},{"pid":"444deab5088dfa9565e16572578b3af37c8657bf","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31143ff82fe7c3780b85198b1c1eaa5f7f71623b","tid":2100051,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:25:41.000Z","msg":"諗下諗下 其實外國國旗當衫著出街都幾好睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"= ="},{"pid":"f0ccc4035a9f1a60ecb861aad06ff5b453606188","tid":2100051,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:26:19.000Z","msg":"不過推下先"},{"pid":"f0bbab7bb57911c581a395080f214d12050cdd53","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:30:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be9732bb5203353e56461f668bd563f15b4698a3","tid":2100051,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:32:04.000Z","msg":"初選宣傳不足，快閃文宣開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2100039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2100039</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af47113937e770b1fdfbe15db82cab9036c289c6","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep