Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e1b14dd3101bcee4ffdde3d3444a7ddd4fdaa6a","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T19:51:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"302a6f87f950ecb71ab6172925431f8f19c8a6be","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T20:00:45.000Z","msg":"等起身再推"},{"pid":"be0c6f9fff185629f935bea7f67cc1a1d784045e","tid":2100051,"uid":218242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T20:41:57.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c085caf210c0633036d97412fda89a4a2ddef296","tid":2100051,"uid":285195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T20:46:24.000Z","msg":"正解！班5毛熱普城喺連登4出帶風向話咩死守香港移民正契弟，推人去死"},{"pid":"f233968d33b078fcd8f39db405a3ccfcf34528a9","tid":2100051,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T21:16:06.000Z","msg":"推！真心推<br />\n請咪再俾popo咬"},{"pid":"da5bf4a89d7179130c502b2a2425481367712789","tid":2100051,"uid":237171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T21:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e058ac38000c6b9f77b8f646b844c7f6b1ec2569","tid":2100051,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T21:35:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af327daebec32d8091d8fd5d17759b63099a65a8","tid":2100051,"uid":190332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T21:43:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c276421e163b5d9adb1d0cb9229c882a63a020b","tid":2100051,"uid":326037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5666fee8aeac861fcb3848cd4b8fa15bed30ba4","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">前言</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢一年我哋抗爭行動嘅目標不嬲都係攬炒<br />\n我並唔認為掟汽油彈就可以成功結束中共統治。我哋遊行我哋勇武我哋開花，最終都係圍繞住一個方針，製造壓力，製造憲政、管治同經濟危機。<br />\n<br />\n國安法就係我哋製造呢三個危機後所達致令中共撕爛塊面嘅終極後果。對唔住，香港人真係無能力逼出解放軍啦，但國安法仍然係一張通往「攬炒」嘅單程票，大家會唔會接受到袋住先？<br />\n<br />\n我哋再上街係為咗咩，再製造一次憲政同管治危機？我認為再製造更多嘅憲政同管治危機，對於出咗宇宙中共維護法都唔會再逼得出啲咩。我唔會同你講上定唔上，但有更重要嘅事要做。<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊要做嘅應該全力同中共進行經濟戰，走資<del>走人</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加速加速再加速，進行<strong><span class=\"x-large\">海外遊說，接觸當地支持我哋嘅民間團體同議員，以當地人身份製作以當地人為本位講中共存在對當地人嘅禍害嘅宣傳影片。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">正文</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我認為從頭到尾，香港人有香港人嘅責任其他國家嘅人有其他國家嘅人嘅責任。<br />\n<br />\n中國唔單止危害香港人嘅自由同人權，佢仲危害住世界所有人<br />\n<br />\n由<br />\n一帶一路債務陷阱外交<br />\n加拿大人質外交<br />\n澳洲國家級網絡攻擊<br />\n滲入美國媒體，影響大選<br />\n盜取知識產權<br />\n台海危機<br />\n南海軍事化<br />\n18國土地爭端<br />\n宇宙中共維護法<br />\n湄公河水壩下遊乾旱<br />\n低人權優勢，令各國產業流失，造成失業造成勞工利益受損<br />\n甚至乎惡意隱瞞疫情，中國境内停航，但國際航班keep going，做成全球50萬人死亡，講緊嘅係我哋200萬人嘅4份1<br />\n<br />\n如果種種以上都無辦法令各國下定決心，唔通死10萬個香港人，就會令各國下定決心？<br />\n<br />\n我哋香港人好可能最終會被消滅，而世界人民最終都係會承受到綏靖中共所帶嚟嘅苦果，世界人民係時候為捍衛佢哋自己嘅價值，捍衛佢嘅自己嘅生活方式而作出選擇。<br />\n<br />\n我哋要改變，我哋唔應該再話香港人點慘，而係接觸當地支持我哋嘅民間團體，接觸當哋支持我哋嘅議員，用佢哋嘅身份，用佢哋嘅媒體，企係佢哋嘅立場，話比佢哋知佢哋要正視呢件事。係一件關乎佢哋自己嘅事，而唔係一個遙遠東亞土地上嘅事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T23:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwvAtHe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwvAtHe.png&h=45e9ca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVKhG2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVKhG2e.png&h=74044050&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce4971c86cb51d2a00b90fa72d1a3d242dc9c0dc","tid":2100051,"uid":3406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e85d739d23352e100eb92298ec4731dfce29a4ab","tid":2100051,"uid":154486,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:56:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">要打國際線<br />\n<strong>要加要初選出黎投票</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有民意backup既人，出黎國際講野都大聲D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf327d8762f1815f5e6665e8a9ce57fed1980e69","tid":2100051,"uid":358248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e445b2a94004e631632ffd1f944736ca8ccf1ca","tid":2100051,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:52:22.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cc4496ee35c6a492022809be47d2c6ba194c8d","tid":2100051,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:16:41.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\nBruce Lee: Do not concentrate on the finger or you will miss out all the heavenly glory"},{"pid":"50661c842f922539e75ffd004e934925010b8dcf","tid":2100051,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:18:00.000Z","msg":"Nicely said<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1544b28862eefb41566f9b27c5f9e1005636e233","tid":2100051,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"起身推一推"},{"pid":"e61d6fd171e8a2d92176f613d026ca17b007334e","tid":2100051,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img